---
const footerLinks = {
  services: [
    { href: '/services#foot', label: '腳底按摩' },
    { href: '/services#body', label: '全身指壓' },
    { href: '/services#oil', label: '精油油壓' },
    { href: '/services#shoulder', label: '肩頸舒壓' },
  ],
  about: [
    { href: '/about', label: '品牌故事' },
    { href: '/about#team', label: '專業團隊' },
    { href: '/environment', label: '環境展示' },
  ],
  info: [
    { href: '/contact', label: '聯絡我們' },
    { href: '/contact#faq', label: '常見問題' },
    { href: '/sitemap-index.xml', label: '網站地圖' },
  ],
};
---

<footer class="bg-stone-950 border-t border-stone-800/50">
  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-900/30 via-stone-900 to-gold-900/30 border-b border-gold-800/20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gold-300 mb-2">立即預約您的放鬆時光</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-400">24小時營業，隨時為您服務。專業師傅，舒適環境。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a href="tel:+886-2-XXXX-XXXX" class="btn-primary flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            電話預約
          </a>
          <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/~@goldenfinger" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-outline flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg>
            LINE 預約
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Footer -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-600 flex items-center justify-center text-stone-950 font-bold text-xl">金</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-gold-300 font-bold text-xl">金手指按摩</h4>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs tracking-wider">GOLDEN FINGER MASSAGE</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          專業24小時按摩養生會館，提供腳底按摩、全身指壓、精油油壓等專業服務。以客為尊，以人為貴。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/goldenfinger.massage" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-stone-800 flex items-center justify-center text-stone-400 hover:bg-gold-600 hover:text-stone-950 transition-all" aria-label="Facebook">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/~@goldenfinger" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-stone-800 flex items-center justify-center text-stone-400 hover:bg-green-600 hover:text-white transition-all" aria-label="LINE">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/goldenfinger.massage" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-stone-800 flex items-center justify-center text-stone-400 hover:bg-pink-600 hover:text-white transition-all" aria-label="Instagram">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services -->
      <div>
        <h5 class="text-gold-400 font-semibold mb-4">服務項目</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {footerLinks.services.map(link => (
            <li><a href={link.href} class="text-stone-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors text-sm">{link.label}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- About -->
      <div>
        <h5 class="text-gold-400 font-semibold mb-4">關於我們</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {footerLinks.about.map(link => (
            <li><a href={link.href} class="text-stone-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors text-sm">{link.label}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Info -->
      <div>
        <h5 class="text-gold-400 font-semibold mb-4">聯絡資訊</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            <span class="text-stone-400 text-sm">台北市XX區XX路XX號</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="text-gold-500 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            <a href="tel:+886-2-XXXX-XXXX" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors text-sm">02-XXXX-XXXX</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="text-gold-500 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            <span class="text-stone-400 text-sm">24小時營業全年無休</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-stone-800/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs text-center md:text-left">
        &copy; 2026 金手指按摩 Golden Finger Massage. All rights reserved. 
        <span class="hidden sm:inline">|</span> 
        <a href="/privacy/" class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">隱私政策</a>
        <span class="mx-2">|</span>
        <a href="/terms/" class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">使用條款</a>
      </p>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-xs">
        本網站僅供放鬆舒壓，非醫療行為。效果因人而異。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
